1
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:16,024
Please come out,

2
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:18,270
I see you.

3
00:01:20,006 --> 00:01:22,369
Coming out all alone like this,

4
00:01:22,930 --> 00:01:25,433
what would you do if you were in danger?

5
00:01:25,458 --> 00:01:26,652
But I am perfectly fine.

6
00:01:30,615 --> 00:01:32,215
I am only doing my duty.

7
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,172
Please do not be so stubborn.

8
00:01:35,310 --> 00:01:37,858
Can you not even handle this much?

9
00:01:38,580 --> 00:01:41,040
How can you truly protect me?

10
00:01:45,570 --> 00:01:47,347
I am simply worried about you.

11
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:50,369
I am fine now,

12
00:01:50,393 --> 00:01:51,618
you can stop worrying.

13
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,815
I like wild flowers.

14
00:02:14,740 --> 00:02:16,129
They are free.

15
00:02:19,870 --> 00:02:21,520
They don't need anyone to care for them,

16
00:02:22,810 --> 00:02:26,910
yet they can still grow and blossom beautifully.

17
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,686
Unlike me...

18
00:02:36,270 --> 00:02:40,523
who cannot find even a moment of freedom.

19
00:02:59,930 --> 00:03:00,886
What are you doing?

20
00:03:03,790 --> 00:03:04,449
You...

21
00:03:06,406 --> 00:03:07,366
Don't move.

22
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:28,720
I only did it because I saw you were in danger.

23
00:03:36,020 --> 00:03:37,329
You touched me again.

24
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:44,701
Or is this just your way of "taking care" of me?

25
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:49,507
I am merely doing my duty.

26
00:03:51,347 --> 00:03:52,326
Is that so?

27
00:03:57,556 --> 00:04:01,452
In that case, go find a Sita flower for me.

28
00:04:04,050 --> 00:04:07,150
Sita flowers don't grow around these parts.

29
00:04:07,500 --> 00:04:09,421
Besides, it isn't even the rainy season.

30
00:04:11,170 --> 00:04:13,015
If you can't find one for me,

31
00:04:13,610 --> 00:04:16,947
I will tell my dad that you aren't taking good care of me.

32
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,212
I'll be waiting for you at the house.

33
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,935
Oh, you...

34
00:04:34,930 --> 00:04:36,184
Always ordering people around,

35
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:38,843
always playing tricks.

36
00:04:41,130 --> 00:04:42,424
Stubborn than a child,,,

37
00:04:45,470 --> 00:04:49,815
Yet as delicate as...

38
00:04:57,735 --> 00:04:58,664
A Sita flower!

39
00:05:03,144 --> 00:05:04,387
Lady Rinkham...

40
00:05:08,307 --> 00:05:09,144
Rinkham!

41
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:14,978
Rinkham!

42
00:05:17,100 --> 00:05:18,664
I'm not playing around anymore!

43
00:05:21,610 --> 00:05:22,406
Boo!!

44
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:28,098
Whaaa

45
00:05:56,650 --> 00:05:57,606
I’m sorry.

46
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:59,378
I'm sorry for being so disrespectful to you.

47
00:06:02,060 --> 00:06:05,421
I only wanted to scare you like a ghost for fun.

48
00:06:06,810 --> 00:06:10,541
You certainly get startled easily.

49
00:06:11,210 --> 00:06:12,793
I’ve seen you ever since I got back.

50
00:06:19,850 --> 00:06:22,609
I have brought you the Sita flowers you wanted.

51
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:24,738
Are you satisfied now?

52
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:29,144
You actually managed to find them?

53
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:33,396
Even though Sita flowers barely bloom during this season?

54
00:06:40,621 --> 00:06:45,150
You really... love finding pointless ways to tease me.

55
00:06:48,707 --> 00:06:50,043
If you can't stand it,

56
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,270
you can still leave, you know, Kaew.

57
00:08:57,350 --> 00:09:01,495
Besides, you look quite cute when you're being teased.

58
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:05,027
If that’s the case,

59
00:09:06,110 --> 00:09:08,646
I guess I’ll just have to keep teasing you more often from now on.
